---
title: Mediterranean Lamb Meatballs on Couscous with Spinach and Feta
description: Saucy lamb meatballs spill over a comforting bowl of couscous in this easy, flavourful and fun meal. Turkish spices add extra warmth to brighten up those chilly days!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-dagneau-a-la-mediterraneenne-39fe8931.jpg
